Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:19.13,头曲-日,,0000,0000,0000,,走れ　Sleepless challenger [You don't stop]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:21.81,头曲-日,,0000,0000,0000,,今に生きる　理由を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:24.85,头曲-日,,0000,0000,0000,,夢尽きないQuest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:27.21,头曲-日,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh[Let's go] Oh[Let's go]
